name: Yield GATA
description: GATA Yield DAO is a decentralized, community-governed organization focused on sustainable yield generation and resource allocation. Governed by yGATA stakers, GATA Yield DAO is committed to long-term value growth and to support aligned projects in Cosmos/IBC, with decisions made through open and verifiable governance. Designed for equitable participation, GATA Yield DAO prioritizes community benefits and financial sustainability.
